<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[put chicken ingredients in cavity, marinate in fridge 1 hr]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[tie chicken, making a handle]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[boil water, dip chicken 5 times, 1 m each, then lift out]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[drain ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[fill a pot with cold water and ice cube, then dip chicken in it 1 m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[make a pot for re-boiling chicke, do the 5 time dipping again, this time afterwards leave in and bring to boil]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[remove pot from heat but leave chicken in, 25 30 m. Test if cooked by inserting skewer in tights, no coloured juoices should come out]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[remove and leave to cool]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
mix sald ingredients, rubbing them in together, and stand 20 m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[make dressing by mixing all ingredients]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
only use the breast of the chicken. shred with your finger in thin strands then coat in sesame oil]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[serve over the salad with the dressing on top]]></step>
</directions>
